{"tid":2081351,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"iOS 14 揭露「抖音」一直在看用戶「輸入的」字","createTime":"2020-06-27T06:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T08:57:50.000Z","uid":66271,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bd243e9407b22a3ff7018270afb1d35d48b3a8ea","tid":2081351,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T06:57:51.000Z","msg":"「抖音」TikTok 除了在中國火熱外，在全球多地包括美國也相當受歡迎，已成為非遊戲類應用之中，下載量最高的 App。<br />\n<br />\n不過由於 TikTok 是中國開發，很多人對其私隱保護感到憂慮，然而又找不到證據。不過，iOS 14 Beta 1 推出後，其保安新機制會顯示一些第三方應用在背後做的事情。<br />\n<br />\n來自 Emojipedia 的 Jeremy Burge 的發現，TikTok 會頻繁地在 iOS 背後存取「剪貼簿」（即 Copy &amp; Paste 的暫存空間）。Jeremy Burge 在 Instagram 測試，當他在 Instagram 輸入一些回應時，每當輸入 1-3 個字元便看到 iOS 14 發出提示，發現 TikTok 在背後讀取用戶的「剪貼簿」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/ScreenShot190526013126-445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2FScreenShot190526013126-445.jpg&h=93663efc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/copying.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2Fcopying.gif&h=1290f495&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了 TikTok，AccuWeather、Overstock、AliExpress、Call of Duty Mobile、Patreon 及 Google News 等應用也有讀取「剪貼簿」，但只是啟動 Apps 後進行一次，沒有 TikTok 那麼「瘋狂」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1275896482433040386\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1275896482433040386&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=b8e267a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1275896482433040386&h=39a3fd87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/i/status/1275896482433040386</a>"},{"pid":"c7c585f073234bf12f2c0e44f729ccc9f1e4b070","tid":2081351,"uid":165749,"like":2,"dislike":0,